{"id": "1405864670040035399", "channel_id": "1405864369371349072", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "We also added a new QoL feature: you can now long-press any card in the Awakener information interface to enlarge it and read the full text.", "timestamp": "2025-08-15T10:44:17.040000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405864369371349072", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜 本地化日志第二期 Morimens Localization Notes #2", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1405864711911768066", "channel_id": "1405864369371349072", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "We know this update also created some new issues, like text cutoffs and awkward line breaks. \nWith the V2.3.1 Update, we've:\n**Fixed the text cutoffs and overlaps; **", "timestamp": "2025-08-15T10:44:27.023000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405864369371349072", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜 本地化日志第二期 Morimens Localization Notes #2", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1405864843524968590", "channel_id": "1405864369371349072", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "**Improved the line break display mechanism:**\nNow, when a line is too long, it automatically scrolls down to reveal the full text, instead of getting abruptly cut off. The issue of longer Awakener voiceline subtitles not displaying in full has also been fixed.", "timestamp": "2025-08-15T10:44:58.402000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-15T10:45:46.094000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405864369371349072", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜 本地化日志第二期 Morimens Localization Notes #2", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
